  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Residence les Balcons apartments are offered on a self-catering board basis and provide you with a fully equipped kitchenette and supermarket within the residence building.</p>
<p>There is also a restaurant on site - L'Auberge - that serves savoy and Italian specialities. If you opt for half board then your meals will take place in this restaurant. Breakfast is served from 7:30 - 10am. Dinner is a set menu that has a starter, main and dessert, and this is served from 6:30 - 9:30pm.</p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with Huski who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a data-udi="umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575" href="/{localLink:umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575}" title="Huski - food &amp; drink delivery service">here</a> for further details.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
