  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the heart of one of the biggest ski areas in the world, <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">The Three Valleys</a>, Residence les Balcons sits in a quiet neighbourhood just outside the resort centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a>. These apartments provide comfort and privacy for your winter holiday and all have picturesque views of the valley and surrounding snowy peaks. </p>
<h2>A fantastic choice for families </h2>
<p>Due to their quiet location, these apartments are a great choice for families. Cots and high chairs are available upon request, free of charge, and there is also a children's pool available - a good way of keeping the children entertained after a day on the slopes. </p>
<h2>Sit back and relax</h2>
<p>Head over to the spa and wellness area for a moment of relaxation. Over <span>600m², Residence les Balcons spa area provides you with an indoor heated swimming pool with amazing views of the valley, a sauna, hammam and a fitness room. </span>Access to these facilities is included so you can really make the most of recharging after an active day but if you'd prefer a massage or treatment, there are 2 spas where these services can be requested and paid for locally. </p>
<h2>Stress free skiing and snowboarding</h2>
<p>Your snow sports holiday couldn't be more stress free as the ski hire and maintenance shop is located 2 minute walk from the residence building meaning picking up and returning equipment is simple and easy!</p>]]></description>
