  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Made up of six alpine chalet buildings, Residence les Balcons is located at the top of Val Thorens resort and overlooks the valley with panoramic views of the mountains. These self catered apartments are spacious and comfortable and provide you with access to a number of spa facilities including a heated swimming pool and sauna. </p>]]></listingDescription>
