  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments </strong>sleep two to four people and are around 33<span>m²</span>. These apartments have one twin bedroom and a pull out sofa bed in the lounge. There is also a bathroom with hydrotherapy tub and a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments </strong>sleep two to six people and are around 52<span>m²</span>. These apartments have two twin bedrooms and a pull out sofa bed in the lounge. There is also a bathroom with hydrotherapy tub, a separate shower room and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments </strong>sleep three to eight people and are around 72<span>m²</span>. These apartments have three twin bedrooms and a pull out sofa bed in the lounge. There is also a bathroom with hydrotherapy tub, a shower room, two separate toilets and a balcony. </p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival apart from sofa beds. An end of stay clean is included except the kitchen. One linen set with towels is included per person, per week.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with a fridge, oven, induction cooker, toaster, kettle, coffee making facilities, dishwasher, cleaning kit and utensils</li>
<li>Lounge area with balcony access</li>
<li>Satellite TV with English speaking channels </li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Bed linen</li>
<li>Towels </li>
<li>Bathroom with bath or shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
